General.Name: Anhui Jiuhuashan Tourism Dvlp
General.Description: Anhui Jiuhuashan Tourism Development Co., Ltd. provides tourism services in the People's Republic of China. The company is involved in the cable car, hotel, travel agency, and passenger transport businesses. It also provides transport and sightseeing services, tourist vehicle leasing services, and operates an online tourism platform. The company was founded in 2000 and is based in Chizhou, the People's Republic of China.
